Quick Reference Rules
Universal Rules (Both Stacks)

Components: Always PascalCase (UserProfile.tsx)
Hooks: Always start with use + PascalCase (useAuth.ts)
Types/Interfaces: PascalCase (User.ts, ApiResponse.ts)
Constants: SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE or camelCase in files
Test files: Same name + .test. or .spec. (Button.test.tsx)

File Extensions

TypeScript Components: .tsx
TypeScript Logic: .ts
JavaScript Components: .jsx
JavaScript Logic: .js
Styles: .css, .scss, .module.css